    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Weapon Type: Kunai You gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this chakra-infused weapon.</p><p>You can use an action to cause thick, black poison to coat the blade.</p><p>The poison remains for 1 minute or until an attack using this weapon hits a creature.</p><p>That creature must succeed on a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or take 2d10 poison damage and become poisoned for 1 minute.</p><p>The dagger can't be used this way again until the next dawn.</p>",
